data.description: Welcome to the epitome of functional living in the esteemed Estonia Subdivision - nestled in the heart of San Antonio's vibrant west side. This magnificent residence boasts one of the largest floor plans, showcasing an expansive layout with five generously proportioned bedrooms + a separate study. With three baths to accommodate every need, along with a distinct dining room for elegant gatherings and a living room adorned with towering ceilings, this home is perfect for both large family gatherings or entertaining.  The primary bedroom serves as a tranquil retreat, featuring an ensuite five-piece bath and a capacious walk-in closet. while the upstairs loft offers a bonus versatile space.  Embrace the epitome of outdoor leisure with your very own private in-ground pool, a rare feature that sets this home apart from the rest. With a thoughtful floorpan and an array of amenities, this home presents a unique opportunity to indulge in both comfort and convenience. Northside Schools.
